article_title: Danny Woodhead's desire and football IQ benefit Chargers

og.description: Woodhead — The World-Herald's male prep athlete of the year for 2003-04 — amassed career bests in carries (106), catches (76), reception yardage (605) and touchdowns (8). He led all NFL running backs with six scoring catches, added 429 rushing yards and returned 12 kickoffs for 262 yards.
